name: Brush Stroke Scarf-Charcoal Black
description:
An original textile design from Dom Streater. 
This scarf is the perfect gift for someone special or a great compliment to your wardrobe.
Non Toxic inks printed on Silky Faille
Luxurious hand and drape 
Wash separately in cool or warm water using a gentle machine cycle. Machine dry using a low temperature setting. If required, use an iron with a light touch on a synthetic setting only. Higher iron temperatures may result in color transfer and melting of fabric.
100% polyester
Baby Hem Edges.
36"x36"
This item ships via USPS priority. 
Please note there is a current waitlist in my shop. Your order will be ready to ship within 9-10 business days!
